# 计算比例函数
def compute_fraction(pct, allvals):
    absolute = int(pct/100 * np.sum(allvals))
    return '{:.2f}%\n{:d}'.format(pct, absolute)


gender_stats_by_user = df.groupby(by = "gender")["user_id"].count()

labels=['男孩','女孩']
values=np.array([gender_stats_by_user[0], gender_stats_by_user[1]])
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei'] 
fig=plt.figure()
sub=fig.add_subplot(111)
sub.pie(values, labels=labels, startangle=90, autopct=lambda x: compute_fraction(x,values))
sub.legend()
fig.suptitle('婴儿性别分布',fontsize=16)
fig.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# 计算每个性别-年龄组合的统计数据
gender_age_stats = df.groupby(['gender', 'age']).agg(
    total_sales=('buy_mount', 'sum'),
    user_count=('user_id', pd.Series.nunique)
).reset_index()
gender_age_stats['gender'] = gender_age_stats['gender'].map({0: 'Female', 1: 'Male'})
gender_age_stats['group'] = gender_age_stats['gender'] + ', Age ' + gender_age_stats['age'].astype(str)
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 12))
plt.subplot(2, 1, 1)

       labels=gender_age_stats['group'],
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90,
       pctdistance=0.85,
       wedgeprops={'linewidth': 1, 'edgecolor': 'white'})

# 添加中心圆使成环形图

fig = plt.gcf()
fig.gca().add_artist(centre_circle)

plt.title('Total Sales Distribution by Gender and Age Group', y=1.05)
plt.subplot(2, 1, 2)
plt.pie(gender_age_stats['user_count'],
       labels=gender_age_stats['group'],
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90,
       pctdistance=0.85,

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 计算每个用户的购买次数
purchase_freq = df['user_id'].value_counts().reset_index()
purchase_freq.columns = ['user_id', 'purchase_count']
freq_distribution = purchase_freq['purchase_count'].value_counts().sort_index().reset_index()
freq_distribution.columns = ['purchase_count', 'user_count']
freq_distribution['percentage'] = round(freq_distribution['user_count'] / freq_distribution['user_count'].sum() * 100, 1)
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))

colors = plt.cm.tab20.colors
explode = [0.1 if i == freq_distribution['user_count'].idxmax() else 0 
          for i in range(len(freq_distribution))]

# 绘制饼图
patches, texts, autotexts = plt.pie(
    freq_distribution['user_count'],
    labels=[f'{cnt}次' for cnt in freq_distribution['purchase_count']],
    autopct='%1.1f%%',
    startangle=90,
    colors=colors,
    explode=explode,
    shadow=True,
    pctdistance=0.8
)

plt.setp(autotexts, size=10, weight="bold")
plt.setp(texts, size=10)

plt.title('用户购买频率分布', fontsize=16, pad=20)
plt.legend(
    title="购买次数",
    loc="center left",
    bbox_to_anchor=(1, 0.5),
    labels=[f'{row.purchase_count}次 ({row.percentage}%)' 
           for _, row in freq_distribution.iterrows()]
)

centre_circle = plt.Circle((0,0), 0.6, fc='white')
plt.gcf().gca().add_artist(centre_circle)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

print("购买频率分布统计:")
print(freq_distribution.to_string(index=False))

4.用户产品复购情况¶

In [106]:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
from collections import Counter
# 计算每个用户的购买次数
user_purchase_count = df['user_id'].value_counts().reset_index()
user_purchase_count.columns = ['user_id', 'purchase_count']
# 筛选复购用户（购买次数>1）
repeat_users = user_purchase_count[user_purchase_count['purchase_count'] > 1]['user_id']
# 获取复购用户的完整购买记录
repeat_purchases = df[df['user_id'].isin(repeat_users)]
# 统计复购用户的特征分布
repeat_user_features = repeat_purchases.groupby('user_id').agg({
    'age': 'first',  # 取第一次购买时的年龄
    'gender': 'first',  # 性别不变
    'category_1': lambda x: list(x),  # 购买的所有category_1
    'category_2': lambda x: list(x)   # 购买的所有category_2
}).reset_index()

# 计算每个复购用户购买的品类数量
repeat_user_features['unique_cat1'] = repeat_user_features['category_1'].apply(lambda x: len(set(x)))
repeat_user_features['unique_cat2'] = repeat_user_features['category_2'].apply(lambda x: len(set(x)))
# 统计复购品类组合
cat1_combinations = repeat_user_features['category_1'].apply(lambda x: tuple(sorted(set(x))))
cat1_combo_counts = Counter(cat1_combinations).most_common()
cat2_combinations = repeat_user_features['category_2'].apply(lambda x: tuple(sorted(set(x))))
cat2_combo_counts = Counter(cat2_combinations).most_common()
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 5))
# 年龄分布
plt.subplot(1, 3, 1)
sns.countplot(data=repeat_user_features, x='age')
plt.title('Age Distribution of Repeat Buyers')
plt.xlabel('Age')
plt.ylabel('Count')
# 性别分布
plt.subplot(1, 3, 2)
gender_counts = repeat_user_features['gender'].value_counts()
plt.pie(gender_counts, labels=gender_counts.index, autopct='%1.1f%%')
plt.title('Gender Distribution of Repeat Buyers')
# 购买品类数量分布
plt.subplot(1, 3, 3)
sns.countplot(data=repeat_user_features, x='unique_cat1')
plt.title('Number of Unique Category_1 Purchased')
plt.xlabel('Number of Unique Categories')
plt.ylabel('Count')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# 准备品类共现矩阵数据
all_cat1 = list(set([item for sublist in repeat_user_features['category_1'] for item in sublist]))
cooccurrence_matrix = pd.DataFrame(0, index=all_cat1, columns=all_cat1)

for categories in repeat_user_features['category_1']:
    unique_cats = list(set(categories))
    for i in range(len(unique_cats)):
        for j in range(i+1, len(unique_cats)):
            cooccurrence_matrix.loc[unique_cats[i], unique_cats[j]] += 1
            cooccurrence_matrix.loc[unique_cats[j], unique_cats[i]] += 1

# 绘制热力图
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
sns.heatmap(cooccurrence_matrix, cmap='YlOrRd', annot=True, fmt='d')
plt.title('Category_1 Co-occurrence Among Repeat Buyers')
plt.show()

# 展示最常见的category_1组合
top_cat1_combos = pd.DataFrame(cat1_combo_counts[:5], columns=['Combination', 'Count'])
print("Most Common Category_1 Combinations:")
print(top_cat1_combos)
# 展示最常见的category_2组合
top_cat2_combos = pd.DataFrame(cat2_combo_counts[:5], columns=['Combination', 'Count'])
print("\nMost Common Category_2 Combinations:")
print(top_cat2_combos)

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 1. 计算category_1的销量和用户数
cat1_stats = df.groupby('category_1').agg(
    total_sales=('buy_mount', 'sum'),
    user_count=('user_id', pd.Series.nunique)
).reset_index()

# 2. 绘制category_1的销量饼图
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
plt.pie(cat1_stats['total_sales'], 
       labels=cat1_stats['category_1'], 
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90)
plt.title('Sales Distribution by Category_1')

# 绘制category_1的用户数饼图
plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
plt.pie(cat1_stats['user_count'], 
       labels=cat1_stats['category_1'], 
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90)
plt.title('User Distribution by Category_1')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# 3. 计算category_2的销量和用户数
cat2_stats = df.groupby('category_2').agg(
    total_sales=('buy_mount', 'sum'),
    user_count=('user_id', pd.Series.nunique)
).reset_index()

# 找出销量和用户数均排名前10的category_2
top_cat2 = cat2_stats.sort_values(['total_sales', 'user_count'], ascending=False).head(10)

# 绘制category_2销量饼图
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
plt.pie(top_cat2['total_sales'], 
       labels=top_cat2['category_2'], 
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90)
plt.title('Top 10 Category_2 by Sales')

# 绘制category_2用户数饼图
plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
plt.pie(top_cat2['user_count'], 
       labels=top_cat2['category_2'], 
       autopct='%1.1f%%',
       startangle=90)
plt.title('Top 10 Category_2 by Users')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# 4. 找出销量=1且用户数=1的category_2
single_purchase_cats = cat2_stats[
    (cat2_stats['total_sales'] == 1) & 
    (cat2_stats['user_count'] == 1)
]

print("Category_2 with only 1 sale from 1 user:")
print(single_purchase_cats[['category_2', 'total_sales', 'user_count']].to_string(index=False))

# 计算这类别的总数
print(f"\nTotal number of such categories: {len(single_purchase_cats)}")

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
df = pd.read_csv('E:/OneDrive/Desktop/淘宝母婴数据集/淘宝母婴数据.csv')

# 按 gender, age, category_1 分组计算总销售额
sales_data = df.groupby(['gender', 'age', 'category_1'])['buy_mount'].sum().reset_index()
sales_data.rename(columns={'buy_mount': 'total_sales'}, inplace=True)
sales_data['gender'] = sales_data['gender'].map({0: 'Female', 1: 'Male'})


sns.set_style("whitegrid")
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))

# 绘制分性别、年龄的销售额条形图
sns.barplot(
    data=sales_data,
    x='age',
    y='total_sales',
    hue='category_1',
    palette='viridis',
    estimator=sum,
    ci=None
)

plt.title('Total Sales by Category, Age, and Gender', fontsize=16)
plt.xlabel('Age (years)', fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('Total Sales (buy_mount)', fontsize=12)
plt.legend(title='Category', bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc='upper left')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# 用 FacetGrid分性别单独显示
g = sns.FacetGrid(sales_data, col='gender', height=5, aspect=1.2)
g.map_dataframe(sns.barplot, x='age', y='total_sales', hue='category_1', palette='viridis', estimator=sum, ci=None)
g.set_axis_labels('Age (years)', 'Total Sales (buy_mount)')
g.set_titles('Gender: {col_name}')
g.add_legend(title='Category')

plt.suptitle('Sales Distribution by Age and Category (Grouped by Gender)', y=1.05)
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

2.绘制饼图（能看到占比更加直观）

In [95]:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

df = pd.read_csv('E:/OneDrive/Desktop/淘宝母婴数据集/淘宝母婴数据.csv')
# 计算每个 gender + age + category_1 的总销售额
sales_data = df.groupby(['gender', 'age', 'category_1'])['buy_mount'].sum().reset_index()
sales_data['gender'] = sales_data['gender'].map({0: 'Female', 1: 'Male'})

# 获取唯一的 gender 和 age 组合
genders = sales_data['gender'].unique()
ages = sales_data['age'].unique()

# 创建分面饼图
fig, axes = plt.subplots(len(ages), len(genders), figsize=(15, 5 * len(ages)))
fig.suptitle('Sales Distribution by Category (Grouped by Gender and Age)', fontsize=16, y=1.02)

# 遍历每个 gender 和 age 组合，绘制饼图
for i, age in enumerate(ages):
    for j, gender in enumerate(genders):
        # 筛选当前组合的数据
        data = sales_data[(sales_data['age'] == age) & (sales_data['gender'] == gender)]
        
        # 绘制饼图
        if len(ages) > 1:
            ax = axes[i, j]
        else:
            ax = axes[j]  # 如果只有 1 个 age，调整索引方式
        
        ax.pie(
            data['buy_mount'],
            labels=data['category_1'],
            autopct='%1.1f%%',
            startangle=90,
            shadow=True,
        )
        ax.set_title(f'Gender: {gender}, Age: {age}', fontsize=12)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
